OL,3,CBritish paraglider dies after getting
OL,4,C'tangled up in power lines' in rural
OL,5,CSpain
OL,7,FA 63-year-old British man has died in
OL,8,Fa paragliding accident in north-east
OL,9,FSpain after he got "tangled up in
OL,10,Fpower lines," according to local media.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for the regional
OL,13,Fgovernment said three fire brigades
OL,14,Fresponded to reports of a paragliding
OL,15,Faccident in Palau de Noguera, a small
OL,16,Fvillage in Catalonia's Lleida
OL,17,Fprovince, at around 1.20pm local time
OL,18,Fon Wednesday.
OL,20,FThey launched a search to locate the
OL,21,F63-year-old, who was seriously injured.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/3
