OL,3,CBritish paraglider dies after getting
OL,4,C'tangled up in power lines' in rural
OL,5,CSpain
OL,7,F"They searched the area, located the
OL,8,Fvictim seriously injured, and provided
OL,9,Finitial medical attention until the
OL,10,Ftwo crews from the Emergency Medical
OL,11,FService (SEM) arrived," the
OL,12,Fspokesperson said.
OL,14,F"Unfortunately, the man, aged 63 and
OL,15,Fof British nationality, lost his life."
