OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781846347
OL,3,CBritish paraglider dies after getting
OL,4,C'tangled up in power lines' in rural
OL,5,CSpain
OL,7,FThe foreign office told ITV News in a
OL,8,Fstatement: "We are supporting the
OL,9,Ffamily of a British man who has died
OL,10,Fin Spain."
OL,12,FThe man's identity has not yet been
OL,13,Freleased. It was not immediately clear
OL,14,Fif he lived in Spain or had gone
OL,15,Fparagliding as part of a holiday.
OL,17,FPalau de Noguera is an hour and a half
OL,18,Fsouth of the Pyrenees mountains, and a
OL,19,Fshort distance from the paragliding
OL,20,Fhotspot of Ager.
